To celebrate our launch at EVEN MORE @walmart locations, we’ve teamed up with @skinte, @rwknudsen, and @quinnsnacks to giveaway a delicious snack pack PLUS a $200 gift card to Walmart to one lucky winner!

Here’s how you can win:

- Like and save this post

- Make sure you’re following @eatbobos,  @skinte, @rwknudsen, and @quinnsnacks

- Tag a friend below (each tag = 1 entry)

Giveaway closes 7/3 at 11:59pm EST and one winner will be chosen at random and notified via DM. Open to US residents 18 and older. This giveaway is in no way endorsed by Instagram or Facebook. The winner will be notified only through @eatbobos, any other account notifying you of winning the giveaway is INVALID. Good luck!

latestPosts.caption:
🌈One of my favorite Pride month traditions- chalk mosaics! It’s such a colorful and engaging way to share our Pride with our local community and I always love the conversation it sparks. For the month of June, @eatbobos is donating 100% of their profits from the sales of the Pride Rainbow Variety Pack to PFLAG NATIONAL with flavors like:

❤️Cranberry Orange
🧡Peanut Butter
💛Lemon Poppyseed 
💚Coconut
💙Original
💜Cinnamon Raisin
 
A yummy and easy way to support our LGBTQ+ community this month. Happy Pride! Say it back! #eatbobos #boboslovespride

📸 @raffinee
